### TESTS DE GESTION D'ERREURS


### Erreur 404 - Ressource introuvable
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/games/999999

###

### Erreur 400 - Champs requis manquants
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/games
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Missing Required Fields"
}

###

### Erreur 400 - Plateforme invalide
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/games
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Invalid Platform Game",
  "genre": "Action",
  "releaseDate": "2023-01-01",
  "platform": "InvalidPlatform"
}


